7\">OPTIMIZED EXECUTION</h3><p class=\"feature-desc\" style=\"font-family:&#x27;Poppins&#x27;, sans-serif;font-size:14px;color:rgba(10,10,10,0.7);line-height:1.6\">Less tokens. Faster responses. No bloated context windows.</p></div><div class=\"feature-card reveal bg-white border-[3px] border-[#068F57] rounded-[14px] py-6 px-6 pb-7 transition-all hover:translate-y-[-4px] hover:shadow-[0_12px_32px_rgba(6,143,87,0.15)] \" data-delay=\"1\"><h3 class=\"feature-title mb-2.5\" style=\"font-family:&#x27;Poppins&#x27;, sans-serif;font-size:clamp(16px, 1.6vw, 22px);font-weight:700;color:#068F57\">2,000+ INTEGRATIONS</h3><p class=\"feature-desc\" style=\"font-family:&#x27;Poppins&#x27;, sans-serif;font-size:14px;color:rgba(10,10,10,0.7);line-height:1.6\">2,000+ apps. No custom API wrappers. Just plug in.</p></div><div class=\"feature-card reveal bg-white border-[3px] border-[#068F57] rounded-[14px] py-6 px-6 pb-7 transition-all hover:translate-y-[-4px] hover:shadow-[0_12px_32px_rgba(6,143,87,0.15)] max-[1024px]:col-span-full max-[1024px]:max-w-[calc(50%-8px)] max-[1024px]:mx-auto max-[540px]:col-auto max-[540px]:max-w-none max-[540px]:mx-0\" data-delay=\"2\"><h3 class=\"feature-title mb-2.5\" style=\"font-family:&#x27;Poppins&#x27;, sans-serif;font-size:clamp(16px, 1.6vw, 22px);font-weight:700;color:#068F57\">SECURE CHANNEL</h3><p class=\"feature-desc\" style=\"font-family:&#x27;Poppins&#x27;, sans-serif;font-size:14px;color:rgba(10,10,10,0.7);line-height:1.6\">Your data stays within your boundary. Nothing stored, nothing shared.</p></div></div><div class=\"features-bottom col-span-full flex justify-center gap-4 mt-4 max-[1200px]:flex-col\"><div class=\"feature-card reveal flex-1 max-w-[calc(33.333%-10px)] bg-white border-[3px] border-[#068F57] rounded-[14px] py-6 px-6 pb-7 transition-all hover:translate-y-[-4px] hover:shadow-[0_12px_32px_rgba(6,143,87,0.15)] max-[1200px]:max-w-none\" data-delay=\"3\"><h3 class=\"feature-title mb-2.5\" style=\"font-family:&#x27;Poppins&#x27;,